The Yakmun clan, which boasted a long time ago, was wiped out in a massacre. The corpses piled up like mountains, and the blood flooded everything like ocean water. Amidst this hell of despair, Sura, opened his eyes: "No one shall be spared. I shall kill everyone. It doesn't end unless I've killed each and every one of them."
Jin Ja-Kang was the lone survivor, and with him a man's lonely revenge, which will be recorded as a legend in the Murimsa Temple in the future, begins!
(Source: KakaoPage, translated)

Jin Yoosung was a gifted surgeon said to be able to bring the dead back to life. However, not even this genius doctor had the ability to revive himself. Following a fatal car crash, Yoosung closed his eyes for what he'd thought was the last time… only to wake up and find that he's been reborn in a fantasy world! A doctor through and through, Yoosung — now Ray — resolves to become a healer again. Unfortunately, it seems his new magical abilities may not be the most fitting for his dream career…
(Source: Tapas)
